\
## Project Overview\
\
This project is a web application for **Frankie's Restaurant**, where users can view the menu, make bookings, manage their account, and save favorite menu items. It also includes features like login, signup, and CRUD operations for bookings and favorites.\
\
---\
\
## Configuration Details\
\
### Server Configuration\
\
- **Backend Framework**: Express.js\
- **Frontend Framework**: React.js\
- **Database**: MySQL\
- **JWT Authentication**: Used for securing API routes (login, signup, account management)\
- **Dependencies**:\
  - express\
  - mysql2\
  - body-parser\
  - bcryptjs\
  - jsonwebtoken\
  - dotenv (for environment variables)\
  - react-router-dom (for routing in React)\
  - axios (for handling HTTP requests in React)\
\
### Database Configuration\
\
- **Database Name**: frankies_restaurant\
- **Tables**:\
  - **customers**: Stores customer details such as `id`, `name`, `email`, `password`.\
  - **bookings**: Stores booking information with columns like `id`, `customer_id`, `date`, `time`, `party_size`.\
  - **items**: Stores menu items with columns like `id`, `name`, `description`, `price`.\
  - **favorites**: Stores the user\'92s favorite items, linking customers to their favorite menu items.\
\
