## Features\
\
- **Login/Signup**: Users can sign up and log in to access their account.\
- **Manage Bookings**: Users can view, edit, and delete their bookings.\
- **Add to Favorites**: Users can add menu items to their favorites (requires login).\
- **Account Management**: Users can update their account details or delete their account.\
